{"tid":1268454,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【請各位善用游擊戰略黎打贏班撐警廢老】","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:53:20.000Z","uid":93536,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ad675398f093382fc70eea9023ba7a82a4ef41","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"1. 點解佢地咁多人？<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收左錢</span></span><br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放假</span></span><br />\n- 追星<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢地目的係咩？<br />\n<br />\n- 挑釁我地<br />\n- 令我地反擊比人拉、比和理非屌、比傳媒寫稿<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣應付佢地？<br />\n<br />\n- 敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。對住呢班有絕對勢力去攪事既人，好應該Be Water立即撤退。<br />\n<br />\n- 第一，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地有警犬幫</span>，無論我地夠唔夠人，情況都對我地不利，任何一條戰線有人被拉都唔值得。<br />\n<br />\n- 第二，佢地都係一班廢中廢老，無我地咁好力氣長期抗爭，平日要返工，放假都唔會日日出黎攪社運。<span style=\"color: red;\">呢家就係要同佢地鬥耐力。</span><br />\n<br />\n- 第三，<span style=\"color: red;\">派錢既活動攪得幾多個</span>，除非藍營同我地搏命玩長期派錢，如果唔係呢啲性質活動好快就收皮。<br />\n<br />\n總之，佢地一進場我地就退，咁佢地就無攻擊目標，紅媒亦無新聞可做。 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然後班廢老返屋企、返工既時候，就係我地進場既時機。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家萬事小心。</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba0b5ec76a21ea3c9b1a52d4e8c7d880f9333699","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9259b369899074f94c792b17510fb7585564d1","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e671b0bb094aa299bd20cb9a5747485447c12eac","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff6b9641dbe8cccc3d2c02d1953db22b8d79cea","tid":1268454,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"推 唔該手足們唔好同廢老正面衝突"},{"pid":"557b0dcdc779a7d03b129c80b0547ca4bc5aa8f2","tid":1268454,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住咁落去真係唔得 唔想再見到多一個人斷送自己生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有無玩過世紀帝國？（發夢想整隻Game)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c734b14ce69226e4bf33f639761487df7f7e0a9c","tid":1268454,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cbe7579ff79356ab2967edb4fa13044964422da1","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae631904ba5d182546c233b9e31b9d967d7a7d2","tid":1268454,"uid":93923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"091e9b91910bb7d5217887c27cc51b3eede4bfaf","tid":1268454,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"同意 exactly 唔好理佢地 好快收皮 大家忍下 唔好中計"},{"pid":"9ff26458e22fe1f88e1da861674e7dfed1f5ae39","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebbde71cb79e3005000548fa4a2f961243fa548","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359bb4c962ec2152fbe5faaee2be880aaa54646f","tid":1268454,"uid":93536,"like":0